---
// blog/src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_URL, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

const pageTitle = `About - ${SITE_TITLE || 'aptcore.one Blog'}`;
const pageDescription = `Learn more about aptcore.one, its mission in the Aptos ecosystem, and the team behind it. ${SITE_DESCRIPTION || ''}`;
const socialImage = "/blog-assets/aptcore-about-og.jpg";
---
<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  image={socialImage}
>
  <div class="py-10 md:py-16">
    <header class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-14">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
        About <span class="text-aptcore-purple">aptcore.one</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-brand-text-secondary mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your dedicated guide to secure and efficient Aptos (APT) staking, built by a team of experienced Aptos contributors.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-invert lg:prose-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p>
        Welcome to aptcore.one! This platform is developed and maintained by a team of passionate contributors within the Aptos ecosystem. Our goal is to provide a secure, reliable, and user-friendly staking service for Aptos (APT) token holders, leveraging deep technical expertise and hands-on experience with the Aptos blockchain.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our core mission is to empower individuals to participate actively in the Aptos network's security and success through staking. We aim to:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Optimize Rewards:</strong> Offer competitive returns for delegators through carefully managed and efficient validator operations.</li>
        <li><strong>Ensure Security:</strong> Implement robust security practices and infrastructure-level protections that contribute to overall network integrity.</li>
        <li><strong>Promote Transparency:</strong> Provide clear, honest information about staking mechanics, including lock-ups, reward structures, and operational performance.</li>
        <li><strong>Simplify Staking:</strong> Make delegation accessible and understandable for everyone, regardless of technical expertise.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why Stake with aptcore.one?</h2>
      <p>
        Choosing aptcore.one means staking with a platform built on a foundation of real-world Aptos experience and technical excellence. Our contributors are deeply engaged in the Aptos ecosystem and committed to delivering value to delegators.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Technical Focus:</strong> The infrastructure is managed by individuals with deep knowledge of the Aptos protocol and validator operations.</li>
        <li><strong>Transparent Approach:</strong> We provide insights and guidance to help users make informed decisions about staking.</li>
        <li><strong>Community-Driven:</strong> We actively participate in the growth and decentralization of the Aptos ecosystem through tools, documentation, and validator services.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Our platform, <a href={SITE_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aptcore.one</a>, is designed to give you a seamless and trustworthy staking experience.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Background</h2>
      <p>
        The aptcore.one team consists of infrastructure operators, open-source contributors, and community members who have supported Aptos since its early days. Our work includes building tools, providing technical documentation, and engaging with the broader validator community.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Educational Resources:</strong> We’ve contributed guides such as “Tools to monitor your validator” and “How to transfer a validator node to another server (no fullnode required).”</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Support:</strong> Our contributors are active on the <code>aptos-labs/aptos-core</code> GitHub and related forums, helping maintain high operational standards and solve complex validator issues.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        This collective knowledge and experience are at the core of what aptcore.one offers.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Get Involved</h2>
      <p>
        We invite you to explore our blog for more guides, tools, and insights into Aptos staking. Whether you're new to staking or a seasoned delegator, we’re here to support your journey.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
